# 🐦 BirdVision – Bird Species Recognition System

BirdVision is an AI-powered bird recognition system built using Python, YOLOv8, and ResNet50.

It can detect and identify bird species from images, videos, and live camera feed with support for English and Sinhala labels.

---

## Features

- Image detection
- Video processing
- Live camera detection
- English + Sinhala labels
- Confidence score

---

## How It Works

1. YOLO detects the bird
2. Crop the detected region
3. ResNet classifies the bird
4. Display result with name + confidence

---

## Project Structure

BirdVision_Local/

- main.py
- live.py
- requirements.txt

models/
- best.pt
- bird_resnet50.pth
- classes.json
- sinhala_map.json
- species_info.json

fonts/
- NotoSansSinhala-Regular.ttf

---

## Setup

Clone the repo:

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/BirdVision_Local.git

Create environment:

python -m venv venv

Activate:

venv\Scripts\activate

Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt

---

## Run

Image / Video:

python main.py

Live Camera:

python live.py

Press Q to quit.

---

## Notes

- Keep models inside models/
- Keep font inside fonts/
- Camera index may vary
